*Grad* je prepun turista u toku leta. (The city is full of tourists during the summer.)

U *gradu* su mnogi znameniti spomenici. (In the city there are many famous monuments.)

On je odlazio u *grad* dva puta sedmično. (He was going to the city twice a week.)

Mnogi ljudi su napustili *grad* zbog nedostatka posla. (Many people have left the city due to lack of jobs.)

*Gradom* su prošli mnogi istorijski događaji. (Many historical events have passed through the city.)